chunks.html_content:
Use this service to unsubscribe from an MOT reminder.

You can also view your current reminders or set up a new reminder.

You have to unsubscribe to stop getting reminders for a vehicle you’ve:

  • sold
  • transferred to someone else
  • scrapped or written-off
  • registered as off the road

You’ll need the mobile phone number or email address you used to sign up for a reminder.

You can also unsubscribe by:

  • following the instructions in the text message you received
  • clicking the unsubscribe link in the email you’ve been sent
